dc_title_s: 2016 National Survey of Community-Based Pharmacists: Use of Digital Health Technology in Practice
dc_description_s: The 2016 National Survey of Community-Based Pharmacists: Use of Digital Health Technology in Practice dataset includes the positive impact that the use of digital health is having on Canadian pharmacists’ changing practice needs and on patient safety and the delivery of care. The survey was done by Canada Health Infoway and the Canadian Pharmacists Association.
